data.description: Welcome to this move in ready 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home with an additional flex room, nestled in a serene neighborhood off of 540A. The property boasts a screened-in pool that invites you to unwind under the sun, while the expansive fenced backyard ensures privacy and tranquility. Enjoy outdoor living from the separate screened-in back porch that overlooks the shimmering pool. With a recently installed brand new roof, this home is ready to insure. There is also a whole house generator, which makes it convenient during Florida's stormy seasons. The interior is equally impressive, featuring an open kitchen with an island, ample cabinet space, and sleek stainless steel appliances. A designated area for a formal dining table adds an elegant touch to the layout. The living space is adorned with a wood-burning fireplace accented by stone detailing, creating a cozy atmosphere. Situated close in proximity to Scott Lake Elementary School and conveniently located near dining, shopping, and more. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to the Polk Parkway, ensuring a smooth journey to both Tampa and Orlando. This home perfectly combines comfort, convenience, and style. Schedule your tour today.
